                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9723" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1462</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">843 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">哈尔滨出圈记——以IP营销为翼的冰雪传奇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Harbin Out of the Circle - A Legend of Ice and Snow with IP Marketing as its Wings</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李晓飞，李雨航</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">首都经济贸易大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">哈尔滨市文化广电和旅游局</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">哈尔滨；IP营销；整合营销传播</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Harbin; IP marketing; Integrated marketing communication</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作为哈尔滨的标志性旅游景点，冰雪大世界一直吸引着国内外游客。然而在2023年末，一场突如其来的退票风波悄然袭来，给哈尔滨的旅游形象带来了前所未有的考验。但哈尔滨文旅并没有选择逃避或沉默，而是迅速采取积极有效的应对措施，不仅成功化解了危机，还让哈尔滨在逆境中抓住了新机遇。独特的IP形象、城市联动、热情服务、媒体宣发……哈尔滨文旅巧妙利用IP营销实现了华丽转身。本案例详细介绍了哈尔滨文旅如何依靠IP营销化危为机，以及如何通过整合营销传播策略制造热点话题，提升城市知名度和对消费者的影响力的。本案例旨在帮助学生掌握IP的概念，理清IP营销的内在逻辑；并通过学习哈尔滨文旅的一系列宣传掌握IP打造的步骤以及整合营销传播的基本理论和方法；最后基于案例，学生应理解如何实现IP的长远发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As iconic tourist attractions in Harbin ice and snow world has been attracting tourists at home and abroad. However, at the end of 2023, a sudden refund wave quietly hit, bringing an unprecedented test to Harbin&#39;s tourism image. However, the relevant departments of Harbin did not choose to escape or remain silent, but quickly took positive and effective countermeasures, which not only successfully resolved the crisis, but also made Harbin seize new opportunities in adversity. Unique IP image, city linkage, enthusiastic service, media promotion... Harbin cleverly used IP marketing to achieve a gorgeous turn. This case introduces in detail how Harbin travel bureau relies on IP marketing to turn crisis into opportunity, and how to create hot topics through integrated marketing communication strategies to enhance the city&#39;s visibility and influence on consumers. This case aims to help students master the concept of IP and clarify the internal logic of IP marketing. And master the steps of IP building and the basic theories and methods of integrated marketing communication by learning a series of propaganda in Harbin travel bureau; Finally, based on the case, students should know how to achieve the long-term development of IP.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《社交媒体营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">IP营销；整合营销沟通</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-07</td>
                            </tr>
